* Make sure that guile-cl is installed, you may find it at
   https://gitorious.org/guile-cl

* Make sure that guile-syntax-parse is installed, you may find it at
   https://gitorious.org/guile-syntax-parse

* Make sure to put this directory in guiles load path.

then use the library by issueing

   (use-modules (stis coroutine))

For examples lock in stis/coroutine directory for example code in eg. test.scm.